WEBVTT

00:00:00.836 --> 00:00:03.793
Some people are obsessed
by French wines.

00:00:04.302 --> 00:00:06.524
Others love playing golf

00:00:06.548 --> 00:00:08.187
or devouring literature.

00:00:08.729 --> 00:00:12.304
One of my greatest pleasures
in life is, I have to admit,

00:00:12.328 --> 00:00:13.534
a bit special.

00:00:13.946 --> 00:00:18.914
I cannot tell you how much I enjoy
watching cities from the sky,

00:00:18.938 --> 00:00:20.319
from an airplane window.

00:00:20.916 --> 00:00:23.911
Some cities are calmly industrious,

00:00:23.935 --> 00:00:25.475
like Dusseldorf

00:00:25.499 --> 00:00:27.140
or Louisville.

00:00:27.780 --> 00:00:31.413
Others project an energy
that they can hardly contain,